			<p>
				<b>How can I get more updates, or updates that Windows Update doesn’t offer?</b><br>
				Visit the following Web sites:				
				<ul style='margin-left:40px'> 
					<li><A class='sys-link-normal' HREF='http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkID=21601' target='_blank' >Microsoft Download Center</a><br> 
					Get downloads for Microsoft products. Downloads are available in 30 languages. </li> 
					<li><A class='sys-link-normal' HREF='http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkID=8973' target='_blank' >Windows Update Catalog</a><br>
					Search for updates for servers and other computers using Windows operating systems.</li> 
					<li><A class='sys-link-normal' HREF='http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkID=24459' target='_blank' >Microsoft Office Online</a><br>
					Find updates for the Microsoft Office system, versions 97, 98 and later. Downloads include templates, assistance content, and clip art. </li> 
					<li><A class='sys-link-normal' HREF='http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkID=27098' target='_blank' >Microsoft Premier Support</a><br>
					Learn about Premier Support benefits, including additional updates, such as pre-release software.</li> 
				</ul>
			</p>
		
		</p>
		
